Interface AcscNetwork

All Superinterfaces:
AclfNetwork, EMFPersistable, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, IAclfAreaZone, IAclfElement, IAclfNetAdjustment, IAclfNetFormMatrix, IAclfNetFunc, IAclfNetWalkThrough, IAdaptable, IMultiNet, INet3WXfrElement, INetBranchElement, INetBusElement, INetworkElement, NameTag, Network, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
All Known Implementing Classes:
AcscNetworkImpl
public interface AcscNetwork
extends AclfNetwork

A representation of the model object 'Network'. * ACSCNetwork * Notes 1) for L-G fault, zeq = zdd0 + zdd2, i1 = i2 = i0 * for L-L fault, zeq = zdd2, i2 = -i1, i0=0 * for LL-G fault, zeq = zdd0 || zdd2; i2 and i0 calcualted based * on v1 on the fault point * 2) For 3-phase fault a zfualt can be defined, but for other types of * faults, zfault = 0.0

The following features are supported:

  • Sc Data Loaded
  • Positive Seq Data Only
